race.comment: LARRGADI (1) collided in the run and missed the frame when seventh (23.26) at this track over 400m in a LS6. Can find winning form here. LUKE'S COAL (6) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 300m (17.46). Comes through a solid form race last start. Leading chance. CISCO RIPPLE (2) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Fearless Two (17.51) in a Grade 6. Expected to feature. PAD UP OWEN (8) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.
